print(a)                               0
print(b) 
print(a+b)                             47
# who is new in programming, I would expect this is to be 4 plus 7, 11. 
# that is because as you can see a here actually as a string,a is one 
# letter string, a character, b is another string  it should take this 
# string and place them one next to the other, the concatenation as and I 
# and I have telling you people computer does exactly what you instuct 
